<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Compiler Main Menu</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="public/assets/compiles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        nav {
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        nav li {
            display: inline;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .center {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .auth-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #217dbb;
        }

        section {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        ul {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        ol {
            margin-top: 10px;
            list-style-type: decimal;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Compiler Main Menu</h1>
            <p>Welcome to our compiler service. Choose an option below:</p>
        </header>

        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Main Menu</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <div class="center">
            <div class="auth-buttons">
                <a href="/login" class="button">Login</a>
                <a href="/register" class="button">Register</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="features">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <p>Our compiler service provides the following features:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Support for Python, C, and Java</li>
                <li>Interactive Compiler Options</li>
                <li>Project Tutorials and Examples</li>
                <li>User Authentication and Code Saving</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="get-started">
            <h2>Get Started</h2>
            <p>Ready to start coding? Follow these steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Create an account or log in</li>
                <li>Choose your preferred compiler</li>
                <li>Explore project tutorials</li>
                <li>Write and compile your code</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section class="about-us">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Our compiler service is dedicated to providing a user-friendly coding environment for enthusiasts and beginners alike. Join our community and enhance your programming skills!</p>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Compiler Service. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

</body>

</html>
